{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dffb089307","title":"对《文艺报》转载《关于（红楼梦简论）及其他》一文所加编者按的批注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"24d31b2c9d","index":0,"year":1954,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"dffb089307"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"a264fb48d1","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这句话批在《关于（红楼梦简论）及其他》一文作者署名“李希凡、蓝翎”的旁边。"},{"id":"5d95394e3d","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这句话是针对《文艺报》编者按中“它的作者是两个在开始研究中国古典文学的青年”一句而写的。"},{"id":"8f093ca4b8","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《文艺报》的编者按中说：“他们试着从科学的观点对命平伯先生在《（红楼梦》简论》一文中的观点提出了批评。毛泽东在其中“试着”二字芳画了两道坚线，并写了这句话。2]这两句话是针对《文艺报》编者按中“作者的意见显然还有不够周密和不够全面的地方”一句而写的。"},{"id":"1e9b40a078","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《文艺报》编者按中有一处说，转载这篇文章“希望引起大家讨论，使我们对《红楼梦》这部伟大杰作有更深刻和更正确的了解”，另一处又说“只有大家来继续深入地研究，才能使我们的了解更深刻和周密”。毛泽东在“更深刻和更正确的了解”与“了解更深刻和周密”旁边，画了两道坚线，打了一个问号，并分别批了这两句话。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7a5d98eb4d","type":"title","text":"对《文艺报》转载《关于（红楼梦简论》及其他》一文所加编者按的批注","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"a264fb48d1","type":"paragraph","text":"青年团员，一个二十三岁，一个廿六岁。“","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"5d95394e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"二不过是小人物。2","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"8f093ca4b8","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"1e9b40a078","type":"paragraph","text":"不过是不成熟的试作。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"3042ec3fdf","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"5c1b3f1d84","type":"paragraph","text":"对两青年的缺点则决不饶过很成熟的文章，妄加驳。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"cfe9dc5bbf","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"},{"id":"c6391b056b","type":"paragraph","text":"不应当承认命平伯的观点是正确的不是更深刻周密的问题，而是批判错误思想的问题。B","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307"}],"page":{"id":"ac9ed2293f","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"dffb089307","start":282,"end":283}}}},"__N_SSG":true}